[[cdo:5 nguŏk 1 hô̤ (nùng-lĭk)]] [[zh-min-nan:5 goe̍h 1 ji̍t (kū-le̍k)]] [[zh-yue:五月初一]] {{Lunisolar May}} '''May 1''' is the 1st day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May|12=draft}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|12=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Keichō|de|Keichō|ja|慶長|zh|Keichō}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|de|Gregorischer Kalender|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|公历}} {{ill|1602|de|1602|ja|1602|zh|1602}} {{ill|June 20|de|20. Juni|ja|6月20日|zh|6月20日}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|de|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|zh|德川家康}} ordered the feudal lords to construct {{ill|Nijō Castle|de|Nijō-Schloss|ja|二条城|zh|二条城}}.
== Births == * {{ill|Keichō|de|Keichō|ja|慶長|zh|Keichō}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|de|Gregorischer Kalender|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|公历}} {{ill|1605|de|1605|ja|1605|zh|1605}} {{ill|June 17|de|17. Juni|ja|6月17日|zh|6月17日}}) – {{ill|Yui Masayuki|de|Yui Masayuki|ja|由井正雪|zh|由井正雪}}, a military scholar and instigator of the {{ill|Keian Incident|de|Keian-Zwischenfall|ja|慶安の変|zh|庆安之变}} (died {{ill|1651|de|1651|ja|1651|zh|1651}}). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|12=draft}} 18th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|de|Gregorischer Kalender|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|公历}} {{ill|1733|de|1733|ja|1733|zh|1733}} {{ill|June 12|de|12. Juni|ja|6月12日|zh|6月12日}}) – {{ill|Maruyama Ōkyo|de|Maruyama Ōkyo|ja|円山応挙|zh|円山应挙}}, a painter (died {{ill|1795|de|1795|ja|1795|zh|1795}}).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Kenji|de|Kenji|ja|建治|zh|Kenji}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|de|Julianischer Kalender|ja|ユリウス暦|zh|儒略历}} {{ill|1275|de|1275|ja|1275|zh|1275}} {{ill|May 27|de|27. Mai|ja|5月27日|zh|5月27日}}) – {{ill|Fujiwara Tameie|de|Fujiwara Tameie|ja|藤原為家|zh|藤原為家}}, a waka poet (born {{ill|1198|de|1198|ja|1198|zh|1198}}).
