== Events == * {{ill|Keichō|de|Keichō|ja|慶長|zh|Keichō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|de|Gregorischer Kalender|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|公历|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1602|de|1602|ja|1602|zh|1602|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 20|de|20. Juni|ja|6月20日|zh|6月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|de|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|zh|德川家康|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ordered the feudal lords to construct {{ill|Nijō Castle|de|Nijō-Schloss|ja|二条城|zh|二条城|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. == Births == * {{ill|Keichō|de|Keichō|ja|慶長|zh|Keichō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|de|Gregorischer Kalender|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|公历|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1605|de|1605|ja|1605|zh|1605|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 17|de|17. Juni|ja|6月17日|zh|6月17日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Yui Masayuki|de|Yui Masayuki|ja|由井正雪|zh|由井正雪|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a military scholar and instigator of the {{ill|Keian Incident|de|Keian-Zwischenfall|ja|慶安の変|zh|庆安之变|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died {{ill|1651|de|1651|ja|1651|zh|1651|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 18th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|de|Gregorischer Kalender|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|公历|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1733|de|1733|ja|1733|zh|1733|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 12|de|12. Juni|ja|6月12日|zh|6月12日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Maruyama Ōkyo|de|Maruyama Ōkyo|ja|円山応挙|zh|円山应挙|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a painter (died {{ill|1795|de|1795|ja|1795|zh|1795|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}). == Deaths == * {{ill|Kenji|de|Kenji|ja|建治|zh|Kenji|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|de|Julianischer Kalender|ja|ユリウス暦|zh|儒略历|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1275|de|1275|ja|1275|zh|1275|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|May 27|de|27. Mai|ja|5月27日|zh|5月27日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Fujiwara Tameie|de|Fujiwara Tameie|ja|藤原為家|zh|藤原為家|12=draft|12=d