== Events == * {{ill|Keichō|de|Keichō|ja|慶長|zh|Keichō}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorischer Kalender|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|公历}} {{ill|1602|de|1602|ja|1602|zh|1602}} {{ill|June 20|de|20. Juni|ja|6月20日|zh|6月20日}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|de|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|zh|德川家康}} ordered the feudal lords to construct {{ill|Nijō Castle|de|Nijō-Schloss|ja|二条城|zh|二条城}}. == Births == * {{ill|Keichō|de|Keichō|ja|慶長|zh|Keichō}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorischer Kalender|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|公历}} {{ill|1605|de|1605|ja|1605|zh|1605}} {{ill|June 17|de|17. Juni|ja|6月17日|zh|6月17日}}) – {{ill|Yui Masayuki|de|Yui Masayuki|ja|由井正雪|zh|由井正雪}}, a military scholar and instigator of the {{ill|Keian Incident|de|Keian-Zwischenfall|ja|慶安の変|zh|庆安之变}} (died {{ill|1651|de|1651|ja|1651|zh|1651}}). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保}} 18th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorischer Kalender|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|公历}} {{ill|1733|de|1733|ja|1733|zh|1733}} {{ill|June 12|de|12. Juni|ja|6月12日|zh|6月12日}}) – {{ill|Maruyama Ōkyo|de|Maruyama Ōkyo|ja|円山応挙|zh|円山应挙}}, a painter (died {{ill|1795|de|1795|ja|1795|zh|1795}}). == Deaths == * {{ill|Kenji|de|Kenji|ja|建治|zh|Kenji}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|de|Julianischer Kalender|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|zh|儒略历}} {{ill|1275|de|1275|ja|1275|zh|1275}} {{ill|May 27|de|27. Mai|ja|5月27日|zh|5月27日}}) – {{ill|Fujiwara Tameie|de|Fujiwara Tameie|ja|藤原為家|zh|藤原為家}}, a waka poet (born {{ill|1198|de|1198|ja|1198|zh|1198}}). == Commemorations ==
