'''May 1''' is the 1st day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=|12=draft}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|qq=|12=draft}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Keichō|de|Keichō|ja|慶長|zh|Keichō|qq=|12=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorischer Kalender|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|公历|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1602|de|1602|ja|1602|zh|1602|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|June 20|de|20. Juni|ja|6月20日|zh|6月20日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|de|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|zh|德川家康|qq=|12=draft}} ordered the feudal lords to construct {{ill|Nijō Castle|de|Nijō-Schloss|ja|二条城|zh|二条城|qq=|12=draft}}.
== Births ==
* {{ill|Keichō|de|Keichō|ja|慶長|zh|Keichō|qq=|12=draft}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorischer Kalender|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|公历|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1605|de|1605|ja|1605|zh|1605|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|June 17|de|17. Juni|ja|6月17日|zh|6月17日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Yui Masayuki|de|Yui Masayuki|ja|由井正雪|zh|由井正雪|qq=|12=draft}}, a military scholar and instigator of the {{ill|Keian Incident|de|Keian-Zwischenfall|ja|慶安の変|zh|庆安之变|qq=|12=draft}} (died {{ill|1651|de|1651|ja|1651|zh|1651|qq=|12=draft}}).
* {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=|12=draft}} 18th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorischer Kalender|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|公历|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1733|de|1733|ja|1733|zh|1733|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|June 12|de|12. Juni|ja|6月12日|zh|6月12日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Maruyama Ōkyo|de|Maruyama Ōkyo|ja|円山応挙|zh|円山应挙|qq=|12=draft}}, a painter (died {{ill|1795|de|1795|ja|1795|zh|1795|qq=|12=draft}}).
