'''May 1''' is the 1st day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May (Lunisolar)|qq=}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Taian|qid=Q96759844|1=taian}}{{efn|ja|大安|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taian|1=taian|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q1306255}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Keichō|en|Keichō|qid=Q1328185|lt=Keichō|1=Keichō}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1602|en|1602|qid=Q6727|lt=1602|1=1602}} {{ill|June 20|en|June 20|qid=Q2666|lt=June 20|1=June 20}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|en|Tokugawa Ieyasu|qid=Q171977|lt=Tokugawa Ieyasu|1=Tokugawa Ieyasu}} ordered the feudal lords to construct {{ill|Nijō Castle|en|Nijō Castle|qid=Q1013399|lt=Nijō Castle|1=Nijō Castle}}.
== Births ==
* {{ill|Keichō|en|Keichō|qid=Q1328185|lt=Keichō|1=Keichō}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1605|en|1605|qid=Q6741|lt=1605|1=1605}} {{ill|June 17|en|June 17|qid=Q2672|lt=June 17|1=June 17}}) – {{ill|Yui Shōsetsu|en|Yui Shōsetsu|qid=Q8060473|lt=Yui Masayuki|1=Yui Shōsetsu}}, a military scholar and instigator of the {{ill|Keian Uprising|en|Keian Uprising|qid=Q6383559|lt=Keian Incident|1=Keian Uprising}} (died {{ill|1651|en|1651|qid=Q6956|lt=1651|1=1651}}).
* {{ill|Kyōhō|en|Kyōhō|qid=Q1145048|lt=Kyōhō|1=Kyōhō}} 18th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1733|en|1733|qid=Q6972|lt=1733|1=1733}} {{ill|June 12|en|June 12|qid=Q2619|lt=June 12|1=June 12}}) – {{ill|Maruyama Ōkyo|en|Maruyama Ōkyo|qid=Q405444|lt=Maruyama Ōkyo|1=Maruyama Ōkyo}}, a painter (died {{ill|1795|en|1795|qid=Q7815|lt=1795|1=1795}}).
== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Kenji (era)|en|Kenji (era)|qid=Q1327993|lt=Kenji|1=Kenji (era)}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1275|en|1275|qid=Q5529|lt=1275|1=1275}} {{ill|May 27|en|May 27|qid=Q2587|lt=May 27|1=May 27}}) – {{ill|Fujiwara no Tameie|en|Fujiwara no Tameie|qid=Q535938|lt=Fujiwara Tameie|1=Fujiwara no Tameie}}, a waka poet (born {{ill|1198|en|1198|qid=Q19750|lt=1198|1=1198}}).
